WEBVTT

NOTE Intro titles, opening animation, signalbox cold open, Spectrum stingers, and closing credits

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
[caption] 'MONTY PYTHON'S FLYING CIRCUS' — EPISODES 17–26 — THE NAKED ANT — A SIGNALBOX SOMEWHERE NEAR HOVE

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:04.500
<v It's Man>
It's...

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:07.500
[action] Opening animation.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.000
<v Voice Over>
I know you're down there.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:13.000
[action] Interior signalbox. A signalman wrestles a bear for 3.48 seconds.

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:34.000
<v Presenter>
Foam at the mouth and fall over backwards. Is he foaming at the mouth to fall over backwards or falling over backwards to foam at the mouth...

00:08:34.000 --> 00:08:36.000
<v Presenter>
Goodnight.

00:28:30.000 --> 00:28:35.000
<v Presenter>
What do we mean by no, what do we mean by yes, what do we mean by no, no, no. Tonight Spectrum looks at the whole question of what is no.

00:28:35.000 --> 00:28:38.000
[action] A sixteen-ton weight falls on the presenter. The 'It's' man runs away. [caption] CREDITS

